data.description: Presenting a delightful manufactured home nestled on just under an acre of land located in Fife Town. Boasting a detached oversized 3-car garage, this property is a haven for hobbyists and craftsmen alike, providing an ideal space for a workshop. The practicality extends with a covered storage area perfect for sheltering an RV or additional vehicles, ensuring they remain protected from the elements. A detached storage shed caters to the needs of gardening enthusiasts, offering a dedicated space for yard tools. Immerse yourself in the inviting ambiance of the house, highlighted by a beautiful sunroom at the front that bathes the interior in an abundance of natural light. Recent upgrades include a modern master bathroom, new flooring, and fresh paint. Meticulously cared for and maintained, t this property extends beyond the house itself. Embrace the freedom of animal rights, the expansive grounds offer a large area perfect for gardening endeavors or recreational activities. This home will cater to your desires for country charm while providing you a blend of comfort and functionality.
